ion>\"\ngit push -u origin <branch-name>\n```\n\n## Step 9: Create PR\nUse `gh pr create`. Check the PR template at .github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md first. \n- Title: \"RECO-678: <short description>\"\n- Target branch: the branch this was cut FROM (check with `git log --oneline -5` to see base)\n- Fill the PR template properly\n\nReturn the PR URL when done."},"uuid":"71d42605-eb79-4bdc-85e9-42891c5fc3dd","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:11:49.964Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/4thwithme/Documents/repo/recommendations-service/.claude/worktrees/agent-a169fe01","sessionId":"847e64d7-967f-4cdf-a9aa-2485dfb21a18","version":"2.1.77","gitBranch":"main"}
